{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-column-to-control-spacing","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi `grid-column` da kontrolišeš prostor","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada, sva svojstva koja su diskutovana namenjena su za mrežne kontejnere. Svojstvo <code>grid-column</code> je prvo za korišćenje na samim elementima mreže.</p>\n<p>Vertikalne i horizontalne linije koje čine mrežu zovu se <dfn>mistari</dfn>. Ove linije su numerisane počevši od 1 na gornjem levom delu mreže i kreću se udesno po redovima kolona i nadole po redovima linija, brojeći prema gore.</p>\n<p>Ovako izgledaju linije na 3x3 mreži:</p>\n<div style='position:relative;margin:auto;background:Gainsboro;display:block;margin-top:100px;margin-bottom:50px;width:200px;height:200px;'><p style='left:25%;top:-30%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;color:RoyalBlue;'>Linije kolona</p><p style='left:0%;top:-15%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;color:RoyalBlue;'>1</p><p style='left:30%;top:-15%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;color:RoyalBlue;'>2</p><p style='left:63%;top:-15%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;color:RoyalBlue;'>3</p><p style='left:95%;top:-15%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;color:RoyalBlue;'>4</p><p style='left:-40%;top:45%;font-size:130%;transform:rotateZ(-90deg);position:absolute;'>Linije redova</p><p style='left:-10%;top:-10%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;'>1</p><p style='left:-10%;top:21%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;'>2</p><p style='left:-10%;top:53%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;'>3</p><p style='left:-10%;top:85%;font-size:130%;position:absolute;'>4</p><div style='left:0%;top:0%;width:5%;height:100%;background:RoyalBlue;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:31%;top:0%;width:5%;height:100%;background:RoyalBlue;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:63%;top:0%;width:5%;height:100%;background:RoyalBlue;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:95%;top:0%;width:5%;height:100%;background:RoyalBlue;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:0%;top:0%;width:100%;height:5%;background:black;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:0%;top:31%;width:100%;height:5%;background:black;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:0%;top:63%;width:100%;height:5%;background:black;position:absolute;'></div><div style='left:0%;top:95%;width:100%;height:5%;background:black;position:absolute;'></div></div>\n<p>Da biste kontrolisali broj kolona koje će segment zauzeti, možete koristiti atribut <code>grid-column</code> zajedno sa brojevima redova gde želite da taj deo počinje i na kojem se završava.</p>\n<p>Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">grid-column: 1 / 3;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo će napraviti da komad počne na prvoj vertikalnoj liniji mreže sa leve strane i proširi se do treće linije mreže, zauzimajući dve kolone.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a90372638fddaf9a66b5d38","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Neka deo sa klasom <code>item5</code> uzme poslednje dve kolone mrežice.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/cnzkDSr","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301136,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-column-to-control-spacing"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Darasa od <code>item5</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>grid-column</code>.</p>","testString":"const styleElement = document.querySelector('style:not(.fcc-hide-header)');\r\nassert.match(\r\n  __helpers.removeWhiteSpace(styleElement.textContent),\r\n  /\\.item5{.*grid-column:.*}/g\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Klasa za <code>item5</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>grid-column</code> koje uzrokuje da uzme poslednje dve kolone mreže.</p>","testString":"const itemFive = document.querySelector('.item5');\r\nconst colStart = getComputedStyle(itemFive).gridColumnStart;\r\nconst colEnd = getComputedStyle(itemFive).gridColumnEnd;\r\nconst result = colStart.toString() + colEnd.toString();\r\nconst correctResults = [\r\n  '24',\r\n  '2-1',\r\n  '2span 2',\r\n  '2span2',\r\n  'span 2-1',\r\n  '-12',\r\n  'span 2span 2',\r\n  'span 2auto',\r\n  'autospan 2'\r\n];\r\nassert.include(correctResults, result);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"use-grid-column-to-control-spacing","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-row-to-control-spacing","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/add-gaps-faster-with-grid-gap","id":"5a90372638fddaf9a66b5d38","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-column-to-control-spacing"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}